data.description: Escape the hustle and embrace the tranquility of this picturesque 1-acre homestead, a hidden gem just outside Jacksonville in Clay County!  Nestled in a serene setting and adjacent to Blueberry and Deer Farms. This property offers the perfect blend of quiet country living and proximity to city conveniences. Key Features: 4/2, two living rooms, a chef's delight kitchen with all-new stainless appliances and sleek new flooring throughout. Brand new AC units and updated duct work. Two new decks, an above-ground pool, and a charming fire pit - perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long day.  Front Horse Fence. Detached 25x40 huge garage to store your boat & cars and available space for workbenches. Ample parking & additional carport. Schedule a viewing and step into a world of tranquility, modern comfort, and endless possibilities!
